{
  "number": 91,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الشَّمۡسِ",
  "englishName": "Ash-Shams",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "By the Sun and his (glorious) splendour;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "By the Moon as she follows him;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "By the Day as it shows up (the Sun's) glory;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "By the Night as it conceals it;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "By the Firmament and its (wonderful) structure;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "By the Earth and its (wide) expanse:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "By the Soul, and the proportion and order given to it;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "And its enlightenment as to its wrong and its right;-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "Truly he succeeds that purifies it,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And he fails that corrupts it!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "The Thamud (people) rejected (their prophet) through their inordinate wrong-doing,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "Behold, the most wicked man among them was deputed (for impiety).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "But the Messenger of Allah said to them: \"It is a She-camel of Allah! And (bar her not from) having her drink!\"",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Then they rejected him (as a false prophet), and they hamstrung her. So their Lord, on account of their crime, obliterated their traces and made them equal (in destruction, high and low)!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "And for Him is no fear of its consequences.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}